      "recommendation": "Add explicit carve-outs for: (1) NLRA-protected concerted activity, (2) SEC, DOL, EEOC, or other agency whistleblower reports, (3) truthful testimony in legal proceedings, and (4) statements required by law. Consider also whether the clause should be bilateral.",
